{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>会下国际象棋的人都很清楚：皇后可以在横、竖、斜线上不限步数地吃掉其他棋子。如何将8个皇后放在棋盘上（有8 × 8个方格），使它们谁也不能被吃掉！这就是著名的八皇后问题。<p><p>对于某个满足要求的8皇后的摆放方法，定义一个皇后串a与之对应，即$a=b\\_1b\\_2...b\\_8$，其中bi为相应摆法中第i行皇后所处的列数。已经知道8皇后问题一共有92组解（即92个不同的皇后串）。<p><p>给出一个数b，要求输出第b个串。串的比较是这样的：皇后串x置于皇后串y之前，当且仅当将x视为整数时比y小。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"八皇后 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>输出有n行，每行输出对应一个输入。输出应是一个正整数，是对应于b的皇后串。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>第1行是测试数据的组数n，后面跟着n行输入。每组测试数据占1行，包括一个正整数b(1≤b≤92)。<p>","examples":"<input>2\n1\n92\n\n</input><output>15863724\n84136275\n\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1214","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}